title: Howard Stern Wack History Month (Crackhead Bob)
description:
Howard Stern Wack History Month (Crackhead Bob)  (05:59:25)

Hosted by Steve-O, this special focus' on George Harvey, aka Crackhead Bob. A fan-favorite Bob earned his nickname after revealing on air that smoking crack led to a series of strokes that hindered his speech and left part of his body paralyzed. Sadly Bob passed away in January 2016 at the too-young age of 56.
